============================================================
  REVENUE ESTIMATION
============================================================

  Assumptions:
  A1. Position sizes: 1 MW, 5 MW, 10 MW
  A2. Trading fee: 0.04 EUR/MWh (Nord Pool fee schedule)
  A3. No market impact (valid for small positions)
  A4. 365 trading days/year
  A5. Balancing/imbalance costs excluded (~5-15% drag in practice)
  A6. Collateral costs excluded (margin capital earns 0%)
  A7. Model haircuts: 100% / 50% / 25% of backtest P&L
  Sources:
    - Nord Pool fee: https://www.nordpoolgroup.com/trading/fees/
    - Market impact threshold: ACER 2024 Wholesale Market Report
